pageProduct.name: Vita Bubs Kids Bone Health Milk Calcium + Vitamin D3 60 Chewable Tablets
pageProduct.description:

General Information

Vita Bubs Milk Calcium + Vitamin D3 is a premium formulation with nutrients to help build strong bones, teeth and muscle, increase absorption of dietary calcium and support general health and wellbeing in children. With natural vanilla flavour for a great tasting children's formulation!

Vita Bubs is brought to you by Bubs, trusted by Australian families and dedicated to children's nutrition. The Vita Bubs range is based on scientific evidence and is proudly Australian Owned and Made.

Suitable For: 2 - 12 years

Size: 60 chewables

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each chewable tablet contains:
Vitamin D3 (Cholecalciferol) 250IU
Calcium (form Calcium Carbonate) 200mg
Bovine Milk 4000mg

Contains: Contains Lactose, Gluten, Sucralose and Sulphites.

Allergen Contains: Gluten| Lactose| Sulphites

Directions

Children 2 - 12 years: Chew one tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal under adult supervision, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25C. Do not sure if seal under lid is broken or missing.
